<p>
  Spring component classes could be implicitly subclassed and must not be final.

  Kotlin class modifiers like <code>enum</code>, <code>data</code>, <code>final</code> and <code>object</code> are
  effectively <code>final</code> that results to runtime errors.
</p>
<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code>
@Configuration
object MyConfiguration
</code></pre>
<p><b>After the fix is applied:</b></p>
<pre><code>
@Configuration
class MyConfiguration
</code></pre>
</body>
